headline: F5 Strengthens Security Capabilities in the F5 Application Delivery and Security Platform
summary: SEATTLE, April 22, 2025--F5 (NASDAQ: FFIV), the global leader in delivering and securing every app and API, today unveiled broad cybersecurity enhancements to the F5 Application Delivery and Security Platform (ADSP) that significantly improve organizations’ ability to identify and remediate vulnerabilities and threats to AI and other modern applications. These new enhancements enable enterprises to strengthen security for business-critical applications in an increasingly risky threat landscape.
